duties_responsibilities.duty: Develop front-end user interfaces for web-based or other software products, including mobile and web console devices.
Collaborate with back-end development, visual design, product management, and customers.
Code behaviors and functionality for current and future software applications using design specifications.
Assist UI team with designs, design reviews, and design coaching.
Provide technical guidance and mentoring in User Experience designs and refinement techniques.
Analyzing, troubleshooting, debugging, and fixing UI and Server issues.
Contribute to end-to-end system architecture, working with back-end engineers.
Collaborate with UX team, product managers, and other engineers.
Assist with new user interface testing and participate in usability reviews, if needed.
Be responsible for usability research and design in the absence of dedicated usability team members.
